Just some skill ideas



Healing:            Being able to heal a certain percentage of the health.              (Moon?)
Strength:           Increases the damage of the attacks temporarily, +1 per hit.        (Jupiter)
Agility:            Increases the speed of the character temporarily, +1 pixel.         (Mercury?)


Resistance:         Being able to take reduced damage temporarily.                      (Mars?)
Armor:              Behaves like kof 99/2000 armor when taking hits, temporarily.
Invulnerability:    Becomes invulnerable temporarily.                    
No damage AB:       Being able to AB without taking damage temporarily.                 (Venus?)
Super Jump:         Being able to execute a higher jump.
Screen Wrap:        Similar to pacman.
